class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Independent Elections Commission · ALSI 2026</span></a><nav class=\"hidden items-center gap-1 md:flex\"><a class=\"rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition bg-[#0B1F3A] text-white\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:text-[#0B1F3A]\" href=\"/register/candidate\">Candidate Registration</a><a class=\"rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:text-[#0B1F3A]\" href=\"/register/voters\">Voter Registration</a><a class=\"rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:text-[#0B1F3A]\" href=\"/register/party\">Party Registration</a><a class=\"rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:text-[#0B1F3A]\" href=\"/status\">Check Status</a></nav><button class=\"flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-slate-200 md:hidden\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><svg class=\"h-5 w-5 text-slate-700\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\"></path></svg></button></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><main class=\"min-h-screen bg-slate-50\"><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden border-b border-slate-200 bg-white\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,#dbeafe,transparent_35%)]\"></div><div class=\"relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-24\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-blue-200 bg-blue-50 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#153E75]\">Independent Elections Commission (IEC) — ALSI 2026/2027</div><h1 class=\"mt-8 text-5xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-[#0B1F3A] md:text-6xl\">Official Election Registration Portal</h1><p class=\"mt-8 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600\">Official digital election infrastructure for candidate registration, political party submissions, voter verification, compliance screening, and election administration under the Association of Liberian Students in India (ALSI).</p><div class=\"mt-6 inline-flex items-center rounded-xl border border-green-200 bg-green-50 px-5 py-3\"><span class=\"mr-2 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 animate-pulse\"></span><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-green-700\">Registration Open — Closes May 18, 2026</span></div><div class=\"mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-[#0B1F3A] px-7 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#153E75]\" href=\"/register/candidate\">Register as Candidate</a><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-[#0B1F3A] bg-white px-7 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-[#0B1F3A] transition hover:bg-slate-100\" href=\"/register/voters\">Register as Voter</a><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-7 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 transition hover:bg-slate-100\" href=\"/status\">Check Application Status</a></div><div class=\"mt-14 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm\"><p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[#0B1F3A]\">3</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600\">Registration Categories</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm\"><p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[#0B1F3A]\">Secure</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600\">Document Verification System</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm\"><p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[#0B1F3A]\">24/7</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600\">Digital Submission Access</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-50\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-20\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#153E75]\">Election Services</p><h2 class=\"mt-4 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[#0B1F3A]\">Official IEC Registration Modules</h2><p class=\"mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600\">Access all official election registration services through the centralized IEC digital platform. Registration closes <strong>May 18, 2026</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"mt-14 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"flex flex-col rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[#0B1F3A]\">Candidate Registration</h3><p class=\"mt-5 flex-1 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\">Submit official candidacy applications, upload verification documents, and complete IEC eligibility screening.</p><a class=\"mt-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-[#0B1F3A] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#153E75]\" href=\"/register/candidate\">Register Now →</a></div><div class=\"flex flex-col rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[#0B1F3A]\">Voter Registration</h3><p class=\"mt-5 flex-1 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\">Verify voter eligibility and register securely for participation in the ALSI 2026/2027 General Election.</p><a class=\"mt-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-[#0B1F3A] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#153E75]\" href=\"/register/voters\">Register Now →</a></div><div class=\"flex flex-col rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[#0B1F3A]\">Political Party Registration</h3><p class=\"mt-5 flex-1 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\">Register political parties, upload required documents, and submit official details for IEC review.</p><a class=\"mt-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-[#0B1F3A] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#153E75]\" href=\"/register/party\">Register Now →</a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"border-b border-slate-200 bg-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-20\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#153E75]\">Election Timeline</p><h2 class=\"mt-4 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[#0B1F3A]\">2026/2027 ALSI General Election Schedule</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm text-slate-500\">Ref: IEC/ANN/2026-001 — All dates are mandatory. Late submissions will not be accepted.</p></div><div class=\"mt-14 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border p-6 border-slate-200 bg-slate-50\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-[#153E75]\">01<!-- --> — <!-- -->May 8, 2026</p><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-base font-bold text-[#0B1F3A]\">Official Election Announcement</h3></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border p-6 border-slate-200 bg-slate-50\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-[#153E75]\">02<!-- --> — <!-- -->May 9 – May 18</p><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-base font-bold text-[#0B1F3A]\">Candidate, Voter &amp; Party Registration</h3></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border p-6 border-slate-200 bg-slate-50\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-[#153E75]\">03<!-- --> — <!-- -->May 10 – May 20</p><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-base font-bold text-[#0B1F3A]\">Verification &amp; Screening</h3></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border p-6 border-slate-200 bg-slate-50\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-[#153E75]\">04<!-- --> — <!-- -->May 19</p><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-base font-bold text-[#0B1F3A]\">Provisional Voter List Published</h3></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border p-6 border-slate-200 bg-slate-50\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-[#153E75]\">05<!-- --> — <!-- -->May 21</p><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-base font-bold text-[#0B1F3A]\">Final Approved Candidate List</h3></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border p-6 border-slate-200 bg-slate-50\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-[#153E75]\">06<!-- --> — <!-- -->May 22 – May 28</p><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-base font-bold text-[#0B1F3A]\">Official Campaign Period</h3></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border p-6 border-[#0B1F3A] bg-[#0B1F3A] text-white\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-300\">07<!-- --> — <!-- -->May 30</p><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-base font-bold text-white\">VOTING DAY</h3></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border p-6 border-slate-200 bg-slate-50\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-[#153E75]\">08<!-- --> — <!-- -->May 30</p><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-base font-bold text-[#0B1F3A]\">Official Results Declaration</h3></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-slate-50\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-20\"><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 p-10\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-amber-700\">Official IEC Notice — Ref: IEC/ANN/2026-001</p><h2 class=\"mt-4 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[#0B1F3A]\">Compliance &amp; Verification Requirements</h2><p class=\"mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-700\">All applicants must provide valid and accurate information during registration. Fraudulent submissions, fake payment confirmations, duplicate applications, or falsified documents may result in immediate disqualification and further IEC action under the Electoral Compliance Framework (Ref: IEC/CPF/2026-003).</p><div class=\"mt-6 text-sm text-slate-600\"><p>Official IEC Email: <strong>alsiiec048@gmail.com</strong></p></div><div class=\"mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4\"><a class=\"rounded-xl bg-[#0B1F3A] px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#153E75]\" href=\"/register/candidate\">Candidate Registration</a><a class=\"rounded-xl border border-[#0B1F3A] bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-[#0B1F3A] transition hover:bg-slate-100\" href=\"/register/voters\">Voter Registration</a><a class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 transition hover:bg-slate-100\" href=\"/status\">Track Application</a></div></div></div></div></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t bg-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm text-slate-500 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between\"><p>© 2026 Independent Elections Commission (IEC) — ALSI</p><p>Official Election Registration Platform</p></div></div></footer></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03tfhzrunrhlw.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[7988,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/17qavn_yt9ecp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n3:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/17qavn_yt9ecp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[37457,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/17qavn_yt9ecp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n5:I[22016,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/17qavn_yt9ecp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\ne:I[68027,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/17qavn_yt9ecp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\",1]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/16.v4iiib-dg5.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/media/83afe278b6a6bb3c-s.p.0q-301v4kxxnr.woff2\\\",\\\"font\\\",{\\\"crossOrigin\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"font/woff2\\\"}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"0:{\\\"P\\\":null,\\\"c\\\":[\\\"\\\",\\\"\\\"],\\\"q\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"i\\\":false,\\\"f\\\":[[[\\\"